**FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE**

**Introducing Zeno: PNC Bank's Revolutionary Customer Segmentation Dashboard**

DSI proudly introduces Zeno, an innovative customer segmentation dashboard poised to redefine the banking experience. Zeno leverages advanced machine learning models and data analysis techniques to provide a comprehensive understanding of our customers' behaviors, preferences, and needs.

Zeno doesn't just ask questions; it delivers answers that empower us to enhance our customers' financial well-being. Through predictive modeling, Feature Importance Analysis, Monte Carlo Simulations, Customer Segmentation Algorithms, Time Series Analysis, and tear sheets, Zeno unveils insights that enable us to take action at the right time and with precision.

With Zeno, we can identify when and why customer behavior changes, allowing us to respond proactively and effectively. By classifying customer archetypes, we can structure interactions for maximum impact, saving time, increasing efficiency, and ensuring a consistent and tailored customer experience.

Our management teams will now have access to standardized metrics and insights, enabling quick assessments of portfolio health and areas for improvement. Zeno also guides us through customer life stages, helps determine their current stage, and even suggests strategies to induce transitions, ultimately maximizing profitability.

Zeno's capabilities extend to our relationship managers (TMOs), enabling them to optimize time management through enhanced insights into portfolio composition. This empowers them to maintain existing relationships, foster new ones, and tailor interactions to meet specific customer needs.

